The paper focuses on driving datasets and annotation tools for vision applications, which are typically categorized under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models for autonomous driving, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing for image labeling, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
